---
title: Aubergine Parmigiana with crunchy croutons and melted mozzarella
description: Aubergine parmigiana is a classic Italian dish that hails specifically from southern Italy. It's such a classic, in fact, that it dates at least as far back as the 1300s. Astounding then, that the very same recipe remains just as sought after—and scrumptious—today.
